  title: Visions of The Divine
  description: My Pontiff, I bring tidings of a most peculiar nature. One of our
    most esteemed clerics has been proclaiming that the Beholder Himself speaks to
    him in his dreams, granting him prophetic visions and divine instructions. Several
    of the faithful who have spoken with him are convinced of his holy mandate, yet
    many more remain skeptical. How shall we proceed?
